g:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Permisos de administración activos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:45pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El sistema solicita nombre y código de la nueva bodega, el usuario ingresa los datos [Excepción 1], el sistema valida la unicidad del código [Excepción 2], el sistema crea el espacio de almacenamiento virtual y confirma el éxito.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:44.25pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: Campos incompletos. El sistema solicita llenado obligatorio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 2: Código de bodega ya existe. El sistema solicita un identificador diferente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.3900000000000001;text-align: center